metadata.title: Subsistence Land Use Maps  - ADF&G
metadata.description: Data Type: Subsistence/Traditional Knowledge;  Blueline maps showing subsistence harvest areas for Alaskan communities. Most were prepared as resource maps for Alaska Management Guides.
